DESCRIPTION:Join us on Wednesday\, June 24\, from 4-7 PM at Whispering Vine South Creek for a Klinker Brick tasting featuring Cabernet Sauvignon\, Farrah Syrah\, Old Vine Zinfandel and Albariño.\nTasting Fee: $15 per person (Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded.)\nFeatured Wines:\n- Klinker Brick Cabernet Sauvignon 2022 - Dark plum and cherry with leather\, baking spice\, clove and a long\, structured finish.\n- Klinker Brick Lodi Farrah Syrah 2022 - Cherry\, plum\, chocolate and white pepper with juicy acidity and fine tannins.\n- Klinker Brick Old Vine Zinfandel 2022 - Blackberry\, blueberry\, cinnamon\, vanilla and warm oak spice in a generous Lodi frame.\n- Klinker Brick Albariño 2025 - Meyer lemon\, white peach\, apricot and minerality with bright\, mouthwatering acidity.\nCome taste through Klinker Brick Winery and find your favorite bottle. Buy a bottle from the tasting and your fee is refunded.
LOCATION:85 Foothill Rd Ste 1 Reno\, NV 89511
SUMMARY:Klinker Brick Tasting
END:VEVENT
END:VCALENDAR